<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.5.5">
<l>cātu caṉattai naliyuṅ kañcaṉaic cātippa taṟ</l>
<l>kātiyañ cōti yuruvai yaṅkuvait tiṅkup piṟanta</l>
<l>vēta mutalvaṉaip pāṭi vītikaḷ tōṟun tuḷḷātā</l>
<l>rōti yuṇarntavar muṉṉā veṉcavip pārma ṉicarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who do not frolic in every street, singing the first one of the Vedas</l>
<l>who was born here, putting [his] pretty primordial form of light there</l>
<l>in order to destroy Kamsa who afflicts good folk,</l>
<l>without approaching those who recite [and] perceive, what will humans pray?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
